reviewText: Cute, cute, cute it's my favorite!

This DVD contains ten episodes from The Adventures Of Chuck & Friends cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Boomer The Snowplow
2. Bridging The Gap
3. Brother Borrowing
4. Chuck In Charge
5. Did You Hear?
6. Little Big Chuck
7. Sitter Shenanigans
8. Special Delivery
9. Speed Indeed
10. The Bully
